=================
 puavo-autopilot
=================

Automatic test tool for Puavo desktop sessions.

Copyright: Opinsys Oy 2013
License: GPLv2+
Author: Tuomas Räsänen <tuomasjjrasanen@tjjr.fi>

Runtime dependencies
====================

- Bash (>= 4.2)
- GNU coreutils (>= 8.13)
- GNU awk (>= 4.0.1)
- GNU grep (>= 2.12)
- GNU sed (>= 4.2.1)
- scrot (>= 0.8)
- xautomation (>= 1.07)


# login testing with lightdm:
sudo env DISPLAY=:0 PATH="$(pwd):$PATH" XAUTHORITY=/var/run/lightdm/root/:0 \
     ./login $username $password
